{"settings":"{
  "workbench.colorCustomizations": {
    "[Everforest Dark]": {
      "editor.background": "#1D2327",
      "sideBar.background": "#1D2327",
      "editorGroupHeader.tabsBackground": "#2f373c57",
      "tab.inactiveBackground": "#2f373c57",
      // "tab.activeBackground": "#1D2327",
      "terminal.background": "#1D2327",
      "panel.background": "#1D2327",
      "statusBar.background": "#1D2327"
    }
  },
  "editor.suggest.insertMode": "replace",
  // "editor.stickyScroll.enabled": true,
  "zenMode.hideLineNumbers": false,
  "workbench.layoutControl.enabled": false,
  "markdown-preview-github-styles.colorTheme": "light",
  "workbench.sideBar.location": "right",
  "editor.fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
  "editor.fontLigatures": true,
  "editor.fontSize": 20,
  "html.format.indentInnerHtml": true,
  "python.defaultInterpreterPath": "/opt/anaconda3/bin/python",
  "editor.linkedEditing": true,
  "git.decorations.enabled": true,
  "css.format.braceStyle": "expand",
  "less.format.braceStyle": "expand",
  "scss.format.braceStyle": "expand",
  "javascript.format.placeOpenBraceOnNewLineForFunctions": true,
  "javascript.suggest.completeFunctionCalls": true,
  "notebook.diff.overviewRuler": true,
  "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode",
  "prettier.printWidth": 110,
  "scm.diffDecorationsGutterPattern": {
    "added": true
  },
  "terminal.integrated.copyOnSelection": true,
  "terminal.integrated.cursorStyle": "line",
  "terminal.integrated.fontSize": 18,
  "terminal.integrated.lineHeight": 1.2,
  "terminal.integrated.fontFamily": "MesloLGS NF",
  "terminal.integrated.gpuAcceleration": "canvas",
  "workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
  "workbench.startupEditor": "none",
  "editor.formatOnPaste": true,
  "editor.formatOnSave": true,
  "editor.formatOnSaveMode": "file",
  "jupyter.askForKernelRestart": false,
  "markdown-pdf.displayHeaderFooter": false,
  "vscode-neovim.neovimExecutablePaths.linux": "/usr/bin/nvim",
  "vscode-neovim.neovimInitVimPaths.linux": "$HOME/.config/vs-vim/init.vim",
  // "vscode-neovim.neovimClean": true,
  "workbench.editor.highlightModifiedTabs": true,
  "editor.minimap.enabled": false,
  "editor.inlineSuggest.enabled": true,
  "workbench.editor.pinnedTabSizing": "compact",
  "editor.scrollbar.vertical": "hidden",
  "editor.scrollbar.verticalScrollbarSize": 0,
  "editor.guides.bracketPairs": true,
  "github.copilot.enable": {
    "*": false,
    "plaintext": false,
    "markdown": true,
    "scminput": false,
    "latex": true,
    "html": true,
    "css": true,
    "rmarkdown": true
  },
  "[rust]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "rust-lang.rust-analyzer"
  },
  "[go]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "golang.go"
  },
  "[javascript]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
  },
  "emmet.includeLanguages": {
    "javascript": "javascriptreact",
    "typescript": "typescriptreact"
  },
  "explorer.confirmDelete": false,
  "explorer.confirmDragAndDrop": false,
  "editor.cursorBlinking": "expand",
  "reactSnippets.settings.prettierEnabled": true,
  "editor.lineNumbers": "on",
  "rust-analyzer.inlayHints.closureCaptureHints.enable": true,
  "rust-analyzer.inlayHints.closureReturnTypeHints.enable": "always",
  "rust-analyzer.typing.autoClosingAngleBrackets.enable": true,
  "git.openRepositoryInParentFolders": "never",
  "editor.autoClosingBrackets": "always",
  "window.menuBarVisibility": "toggle",
  "markdown.marp.enableHtml": true,
  "markdown.marp.exportType": "html",
  "latex-workshop.latex.clean.command": "pdflatex",
  "[shellscript]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "foxundermoon.shell-format"
  },
  "editor.wordWrap": "on",
  "color-highlight.markRuler": false,
  "go.inlayHints.assignVariableTypes": true,
  "go.inlayHints.functionTypeParameters": true,
  "go.inlayHints.rangeVariableTypes": true,
  "go.inlayHints.constantValues": true,
  "go.inlayHints.compositeLiteralTypes": true,
  "go.inlayHints.compositeLiteralFields": true,
  "extensions.autoUpdate": false,
  "workbench.colorTheme": "Catppuccin Latte",
  "breadcrumbs.enabled": false,
  "errorLens.messageEnabled": true,
  "window.titleBarStyle": "native",
  "window.customMenuBarAltFocus": false,
  "files.autoSave": "afterDelay",
  "liveServer.settings.CustomBrowser": "chrome",
  "workbench.activityBar.visible": false,
  "codesnap.boxShadow": "#E89B85",
  "codesnap.backgroundColor": "#E89B85",
  "codesnap.showLineNumbers": false,
  "codesnap.showWindowControls": false,
  "codesnap.containerPadding": ""
}"}
